"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-zharnel-hughes-olympics-2024-paris-b2591353.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The Briton was knocked out of the semi-finals of the 100m in Paris and will now concentrate on the 4x100m relay  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Briton\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q25379\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\"}, {\"begin\": 277, \"end\": 282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999983092493, \"rank\": 1.6907835399506031e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  BritishsprinterZharnel Hugheshas withdrawn from Monday night's Olympic 200m heats due to a hamstring issue.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes, the world 100m bronze medallist, came up short of reaching a second straight Olympic final at that distance on Sunday night after clocking 10.01 to finish 14th of the semi-finalists.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He skipped the European and British championships after sustaining a hamstring injury, but was given a discretionary place and before these Games said he was feeling fit ahead ofParis.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 788, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.113991849516785e-20, \"text\": \"British championships\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABritish Athleticsstatement said: \\\"Zharnel Hughes has withdrawn from the 200m heats tonight due to a hamstring tightness which requires monitoring for the next 48 hours.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9980345061748621, \"rank\": 0.0015466843918968446, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No decision has been taken as yet in relation to his relay involvement.\\\"\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes was hoping he could wrap up some unfinished business in Paris, three summers after he was disqualified from the 100m final for a false start.\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9980345061748621, \"rank\": 0.0015466843918968446, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999983092493, \"rank\": 1.6907835399506031e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old was also part of the British 4x100m relay team in Tokyo who were stripped of silver afterCJ Ujahfailed a doping test and was banned from the sport for 22 months.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1408, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9961983040790692, \"rank\": 0.0038161914841664995, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In May, Hughes, \\u00a0Eugene Amo-Dadzie, Richard Kilty and Nethaneel Mitchell-Blake secured Great Britain a relay spot in Paris at World Athletics Relays Bahamas 24.\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1529, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9980345061748621, \"rank\": 0.0015466843918968446, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Kilty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Richard Kilty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Kilty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Kilty\"}, {\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nethaneel_Mitchell-Blake\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nethaneel Mitchell-Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nethaneel_Mitchell-Blake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nethaneel_Mitchell-Blake\"}, {\"begin\": 1608, \"end\": 1621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999882893054255, \"rank\": 0.00011709659837130749, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1638, \"end\": 1643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999983092493, \"rank\": 1.6907835399506031e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1647, \"end\": 1662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999626620101004, \"rank\": 3.7339383982589665e-05, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heats for that relay begin on Thursday morning, though Hughes could also be saved for Friday's evening's final should the British quartet qualify.\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1738, \"end\": 1744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9980345061748621, \"rank\": 0.0015466843918968446, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9792864621044116, \"rank\": 0.020275877967344362, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes was hoping he could wrap up some unfinished business in Paris, three summers after he was disqualified from the 100m final for a false start, the first Briton to reach the blue riband showdown in 21 years.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9980345061748621, \"rank\": 0.0015466843918968446, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999983092493, \"rank\": 1.6907835399506031e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old was also part of the British 4\\u00d7100 metres relay team in Tokyo who were stripped of silver after CJ Ujah failed a doping test and was banned from the sport for 22 months.\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9792864621044116, \"rank\": 0.020275877967344362, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 2117, \"end\": 2122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9961983040790692, \"rank\": 0.0038161914841664995, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2157, \"end\": 2164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Ujah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CJ Ujah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Ujah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Ujah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes was part of the 4x100m men's relay team who, in May, secured Great Britain a relay spot in Paris at World Athletics Relays Bahamas 24.\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2232, \"end\": 2238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9980345061748621, \"rank\": 0.0015466843918968446, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 2300, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999882893054255, \"rank\": 0.00011709659837130749, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2330, \"end\": 2335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999983092493, \"rank\": 1.6907835399506031e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2339, \"end\": 2354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999626620101004, \"rank\": 3.7339383982589665e-05, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heats for that relay begin on Thursday morning, though Hughes could also be saved for Friday's evening's final should the British quartet qualify.\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2430, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9980345061748621, \"rank\": 0.0015466843918968446, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 2497, \"end\": 2504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9792864621044116, \"rank\": 0.020275877967344362, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked on the evening of the Olympic opening ceremony if the injury had shifted his perceptions of success in Paris, Hughes' answer was an emphatic \\\"no\\\".\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999983092493, \"rank\": 1.6907835399506031e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2639, \"end\": 2645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9980345061748621, \"rank\": 0.0015466843918968446, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was more forthcoming after failing to make the 100 metres final on Sunday night, saying: \\\"I am disappointed.\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I gave it my best.\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You all know I had a hamstring injury.\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2846, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is not the easiest thing to come back from, especially what I had, a grade two on the outside of the (right) hamstring.\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Not getting enough races to be race sharp, that was my issue.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything had to be rushed.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the injury you start to get the treatment right away.\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we had more races, you know that I am a better performer than this.\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year we ended with 9.88 on the podium and with a bronze.\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know what I am capable of.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to be battling with an injury.\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It kind of sucks, last minute just before the Olympics, but I am a fighter.\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very determined, and that's why I wanted to give it a go.\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got the training in but the races is what I needed to get me race sharp.\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a competitive athlete, you want to be a part of the mix.\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I rarely miss out on finals, so this is one a bit hard to swallow.\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will just move on from here.\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The road sometimes can be rocky, there are days that you guys do not see the work behind the scenes and injuries that come along.\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We try to give our best.\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today I gave it my best.\\\"\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 4120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3941, \"end\": 3952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.3549199618487265e-13, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"